Eyecube is a sandbox game.

C++ with ncurses and pthreads
Now only singleplayer is developed.

Screenshots of early versions are available here: https://picasaweb.google.com/mmaulwurff/Eyecube?authuser=0&feat=directlink

Advices are welcome.

Some keys (',' instead of 'w', 'o' intstead of 's', 'e' intstead of 'd')
are set for Dvorak keyboard.

